rating results not matching that</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2075787099/image_2075787099.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745722-applied-materials-buy-and-hold-this-stock-for-a-long-time", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 07:22:38", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745720", "title": "Apple Defies Gravity As New Threats Are Not Priced In", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458990823/image_458990823.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Apple Store\" data-id=\"458990823\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4952px\" height=\"3185px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458990823/image_458990823.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458990823/image_458990823.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458990823/image_458990823.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458990823/image_458990823.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458990823/image_458990823.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458990823/image_458990823.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458990823/image_458990823.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458990823/image_458990823.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Nikada/iStock Unreleased via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Apple (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AAPL\" title=\"Apple Inc.\">AAPL</a></span>) stock has shown close to 30% YTD total returns, which is only slightly above the broader S&amp;P 500 total returns of 25% in 2024. Even the recent Apple Intelligence iPhone upgrade has not given a</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458990823/image_458990823.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745720-apple-defies-gravity-as-new-threats-are-not-priced-in", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 07:09:36", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745728", "title": "Global Diversification Is Still Working", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1063745228/image_1063745228.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Woman using a smartphone, next to a futuristic digitally generated display\" data-id=\"1063745228\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1063745228/image_1063745228.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1063745228/image_1063745228.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1063745228/image_1063745228.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1063745228/image_1063745228.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1063745228/image_1063745228.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1063745228/image_1063745228.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1063745228/image_1063745228.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1063745228/image_1063745228.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Bloom Productions/DigitalVision via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>When the stock market booms like this, we inevitably start getting questions about why we shouldn't be 100% stocks.<sup>1</sup> More recently, the discussion has become even more concentrated as US stocks have outperformed international by</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1063745228/image_1063745228.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745728-global-diversification-still-working", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 06:50:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745723", "title": "Markets Weekly Outlook - S&P 500 In Focus As Markets Brace For Holiday Lull", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1936201908/image_1936201908.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Bull market in the US stock market\" data-id=\"1936201908\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1936201908/image_1936201908.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1936201908/image_1936201908.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1936201908/image_1936201908.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1936201908/image_1936201908.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1936201908/image_1936201908.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1936201908/image_1936201908.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1936201908/image_1936201908.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1936201908/image_1936201908.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">honglouwawa</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Zain Vawda</em> </p> <h2><strong>Week in Review: Hawkish Fed Sends Markets into a Frenzy</strong></h2> <p>A week that finally confirmed the long anticipated 'pivot' by the Federal Reserve from a policy perspective. I do not like using the word pivot until the Fed actually</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1936201908/image_1936201908.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745723-markets-weekly-outlook-sp500-in-focus-markets-brace-holiday-lull", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 06:30:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745718", "title": "Unpacking The 'Value' In The WisdomTree U.S. Value Fund", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Little piggy banks on ascending stacks of coins\" data-id=\"1072593728\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5423px\" height=\"3261px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Matt Wagner, CFA</em></p> <p>Anytime a value fund jumps on the radar during a growth-led rally, a natural question pops up: how \"value\" is the fund?</p> <p>In other words, someone would rightly want to know if the fund is \"value-lite\" and</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745718-unpacking-value-wisdomtree-us-value-fund", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 06:00:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745717", "title": "U.S. IPO Weekly Recap: Small Issuers Slip Through The IPO Window Ahead Of The Holiday Week", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2007806404/image_2007806404.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"IPO Initial Public Offering text, inscription. IPO concept, banner. 3D render\" data-id=\"2007806404\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2007806404/image_2007806404.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2007806404/image_2007806404.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2007806404/image_2007806404.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2007806404/image_2007806404.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2007806404/image_2007806404.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2007806404/image_2007806404.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2007806404/image_2007806404.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2007806404/image_2007806404.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">bin kontan</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Four small IPOs priced this past week, joined by one SPAC.</p> <p>The biggest development came from the pipeline, with natural gas exporter <strong>Venture Global</strong> (VG) filing for an estimated $3 billion IPO.</p> <p>The week's deals all came from</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2007806404/image_2007806404.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745717-us-ipo-small-issuers-slip-through-ipo-window-ahead-holiday-week", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 05:35:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745716", "title": "PCE Prints Cool: Validates Our Dovish View On Inflation", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2167608577/image_2167608577.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Personal Consumption Expenditures PCE are shown using the text\" data-id=\"2167608577\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2167608577/image_2167608577.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2167608577/image_2167608577.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2167608577/image_2167608577.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2167608577/image_2167608577.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2167608577/image_2167608577.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2167608577/image_2167608577.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2167608577/image_2167608577.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2167608577/image_2167608577.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Andrii Dodonov/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Core PCE came in at only .11% vs. expectations at .2% and Y/Y was 2.8% vs. expectations of 2.9%. We continue to believe that both investors and the Fed are way too pessimistic about inflation as we are forecasting that core PCE</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2167608577/image_2167608577.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745716-pce-prints-cool-validates-our-dovish-view-on-inflation", "pub_date": "2024-12-21 04:45:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4745479", "title": "AI: Will Freshworks Leave Room For Concentrix?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817371218/image_1817371218.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"AI symbol with speech bubbles\" data-id=\"1817371218\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817371218/image_1817371218.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817371218/image_1817371218.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817371218/image_1817371218.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817371218/image_1817371218.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817371218/image_1817371218.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817371218/image_1817371218.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817371218/image_1817371218.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817371218/image_1817371218.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">J Studios</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>One of the fields most likely to see big impacts from AI is Customer Relationship Management (CRM) CRM is dominated by Salesforce, which has appropriated the CRM abbreviation as its ticker.</p> <h2>So what is CRM?</h2> <p>CRM is</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1817371218/image_1817371218.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4745479-ai-